335class boss_yoggsaron_sara : public CreatureScript
336{
337public:
338 boss_yoggsaron_sara() : CreatureScript("boss_yoggsaron_sara") { }
339
340 CreatureAI* GetAI(Creature* pCreature) const override
341 {
342 return GetUlduarAI<boss_yoggsaron_saraAI>(pCreature);
343 }
344
345 struct boss_yoggsaron_saraAI : public ScriptedAI
346 {
347 boss_yoggsaron_saraAI(Creature* pCreature) : ScriptedAI(pCreature), summons(pCreature)
348 {
349 m_pInstance = pCreature->GetInstanceScript();
350 }
351
352 InstanceScript* m_pInstance;
353 EventMap events;
354 SummonList summons;
355
356 uint32 _initFight;
357 ObjectGuid _keepersGUID[4];
358 uint8 _summonedGuardiansCount;
359 uint32 _p2TalkTimer;
360 bool _secondPhase;
361 float _summonSpeed;
362 uint8 _currentIllusion;
363 bool _isIllusionReversed;
364
365 void AttackStart(Unit*) override { }
366 void MoveInLineOfSight(Unit*) override { }
367
368 void JustSummoned(Creature* cr) override
369 {
370 summons.Summon(cr);
371 if (cr->GetEntry() >= NPC_FREYA_KEEPER && cr->GetEntry() <= NPC_THORIM_KEEPER)
372 {
373 if (cr->GetEntry() == NPC_FREYA_KEEPER)
374 cr->CastSpell(cr, SPELL_CONJURE_SANITY_WELL, false);
375 _keepersGUID[cr->GetEntry() - NPC_FREYA_KEEPER] = cr->GetGUID();
376 }
377 else if (cr->GetEntry() == NPC_SANITY_WELL)
378 cr->ApplySpellImmune(0, IMMUNITY_STATE, SPELL_AURA_MOD_SCALE, true);
379 }
380
381 void SpawnClouds()
382 {
383 for (uint8 i = 0; i < 6; ++i)
384 {
385 float Zplus = i > 2 ? (i - 2) * 1.6f : 0;
386 if (i % 2)
387 me->SummonCreature(NPC_OMINOUS_CLOUD, me->GetPositionX() + 8 + i * 7, me->GetPositionY() + 8 + i * 7, 326 + Zplus, 0);
388 else
389 me->SummonCreature(NPC_OMINOUS_CLOUD, me->GetPositionX() - 8 - i * 7, me->GetPositionY() - 8 - i * 7, 326 + Zplus, 0);
390 }
391 }
392
393 void SpawnWeels()
394 {
395 me->SummonCreature(NPC_SANITY_WELL, 2042.56f, -40.3667f, 329.274f, 0.0f);
396 me->SummonCreature(NPC_SANITY_WELL, 1975.89f, 40.0216f, 331.1f, 0.0f);
397 me->SummonCreature(NPC_SANITY_WELL, 1987.12f, -91.2702f, 330.186f, 0.0f);
398 me->SummonCreature(NPC_SANITY_WELL, 1900.48f, -51.2386f, 332.13f, 0.0f);
399 me->SummonCreature(NPC_SANITY_WELL, 1899.94f, 0.330621f, 332.296f, 0.0f);
400 }
401
402 void EnterEvadeMode(EvadeReason why) override
403 {
404 if (!_EnterEvadeMode(why))
405 return;
406
407 Position pos;
408 pos = me->GetHomePosition();
409 me->NearTeleportTo(pos.GetPositionX(), pos.GetPositionY(), pos.GetPositionZ(), pos.GetOrientation());
410 Reset();
411 me->setActive(false);
412 }
413
414 void EnableSara(bool apply)
415 {
416 if (apply)
417 {
418 me->RemoveUnitFlag(UNIT_FLAG_DISABLE_MOVE);
419 me->DisableRotate(false);
420 me->ClearUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ROOT);
421 }
422 else
423 {
424 me->SetUnitFlag(UNIT_FLAG_DISABLE_MOVE);
425 me->DisableRotate(true);
426 me->AddUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ROOT);
427 }
428 }
429
430 void Reset() override
431 {
432 summons.DoAction(ACTION_DESPAWN_ADDS);
433 events.Reset();
434 summons.DespawnAll();
435
436 me->SetVisible(true);
437 me->SetDisplayId(me->GetNativeDisplayId());
438 me->SetDisableGravity(true);
439 EnableSara(false);
440 SpawnClouds();
441
442 _initFight = 1;
443
444 for (uint8 i = 0; i < 4; ++i)
445 _keepersGUID[i].Clear();
446
447 _summonedGuardiansCount = 0;
448 _p2TalkTimer = 0;
449 _secondPhase = false;
450 _summonSpeed = 1.0f;
451 _currentIllusion = urand(1, 3);
452 _isIllusionReversed = urand(0, 1);
453
454 if (m_pInstance)
455 {
456 m_pInstance->DoStopTimedAchievement(ACHIEVEMENT_TIMED_TYPE_EVENT, CRITERIA_NOT_GETTING_OLDER);
457 m_pInstance->DoRemoveAurasDueToSpellOnPlayers(SPELL_SANITY);
458 m_pInstance->SetData(TYPE_YOGGSARON, NOT_STARTED);
459 if (GameObject* go = ObjectAccessor::GetGameObject(*me, m_pInstance->GetGuidData(GO_YOGG_SARON_DOORS)))
460 go->SetGoState(GO_STATE_ACTIVE);
461 }
462 }
463
464 void InitFight(Unit* target)
465 {
466 if (!m_pInstance)
467 return;
468
469 // some simple hack checks
470 if (m_pInstance->GetData(TYPE_VEZAX) != DONE || m_pInstance->GetData(TYPE_XT002) != DONE)
471 return;
472
473 m_pInstance->DoStartTimedAchievement(ACHIEVEMENT_TIMED_TYPE_EVENT, CRITERIA_NOT_GETTING_OLDER);
474 m_pInstance->SetData(TYPE_YOGGSARON, IN_PROGRESS);
475 me->SetInCombatWithZone();
476 AttackStart(target);
477
478 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_SANITY_BASE, true);
479
480 SaveKeepers();
481
482 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARA_P1_DOORS_CLOSE, 15000, 0, EVENT_PHASE_ONE);
483 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARA_P1_BERSERK, 900000, 0, 0);
484 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARA_P1_SUMMON, 0, 0, EVENT_PHASE_ONE);
485 events.SetPhase(EVENT_PHASE_ONE);
486
487 me->Yell("The time to strike at the head of the beast will soon be upon us! Focus your anger and hatred on his minions!", LANG_UNIVERSAL);
488 me->PlayDirectSound(SARA_AGGRO);
489 me->setActive(true);
490 }
491
492 void SaveKeepers()
493 {
494 for (uint8 i = 0; i < 4; ++i)
495 if (m_pInstance->GetData(TYPE_WATCHERS) & (1 << i))
496 switch (i)
497 {
498 case KEEPER_FREYA:
499 SpawnWeels();
500 me->SummonCreature(NPC_FREYA_KEEPER, 1939.32f, 42.165f, 338.415f, 5.17955f);
501 break;
502 case KEEPER_HODIR:
503 me->SummonCreature(NPC_HODIR_KEEPER, 1939.13f, -90.8332f, 338.415f, 1.00123f);
504 break;
505 case KEEPER_MIMIRON:
506 me->SummonCreature(NPC_MIMIRON_KEEPER, 2036.81f, 25.6646f, 338.415f, 3.74227f);
507 break;
508 case KEEPER_THORIM:
509 me->SummonCreature(NPC_THORIM_KEEPER, 2036.59f, -73.8499f, 338.415f, 2.34819f);
510 break;
511 }
512 }
513
514 void InformCloud()
515 {
516 Creature* cloud = nullptr;
517 for (SummonList::const_iterator itr = summons.begin(); itr != summons.end();)
518 {
519 Creature* summon = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, *itr);
520 ++itr;
521 if (!summon || summon->GetEntry() != NPC_OMINOUS_CLOUD || me->GetDistance(summon) < 20)
522 continue;
523
524 if ((!cloud || (urand(0, 1) && !summon->HasAura(SPELL_SUMMON_GUARDIAN_OF_YS))))
525 cloud = summon;
526 }
527
528 if (cloud)
529 cloud->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_START_SUMMONING);
530 }
531
532 void SpawnTentacle(uint32 entry)
533 {
534 uint32 dist = urand(38, 48);
535 float o = rand_norm() * M_PI * 2;
536 float Zplus = (dist - 38) / 6.5f;
537 if (Creature* cr = me->SummonCreature(entry, me->GetPositionX() + dist * cos(o), me->GetPositionY() + dist * std::sin(o), 327.2 + Zplus, 0, TEMPSUMMON_CORPSE_TIMED_DESPAWN, 5000))
538 {
539 cr->CastSpell(cr, SPELL_TENTACLE_ERUPT, true);
540 cr->CastSpell(cr, SPELL_VOID_ZONE_SMALL, true);
541 cr->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_EMERGE);
542 }
543 }
544
545 void SummonDeathOrbs()
546 {
547 for (uint8 i = 0; i < 4; ++i)
548 {
549 uint32 dist = urand(38, 48);
550 float o = rand_norm() * M_PI * 2;
551 float Zplus = (dist - 38) / 6.5f;
552 me->SummonCreature(NPC_DEATH_ORB, me->GetPositionX() + dist * cos(o), me->GetPositionY() + dist * std::sin(o), 327.2 + Zplus, 0, TEMPSUMMON_TIMED_DESPAWN, 20000);
553 }
554 }
555
556 void AddPortals()
557 {
558 _summonSpeed -= 0.1f;
559 Creature* cr = nullptr;
560
561 // Spawn Portals
562 for (uint8 i = 0; i < RAID_MODE(4, 10); ++i)
563 {
564 if ((cr = me->SummonCreature(NPC_DESCEND_INTO_MADNESS, yoggPortalLoc[i].x, yoggPortalLoc[i].y, yoggPortalLoc[i].z, 0, TEMPSUMMON_TIMED_DESPAWN, 25000)))
565 {
566 cr->SetUnitFlag(UNIT_FLAG_DISABLE_MOVE | UNIT_FLAG_NON_ATTACKABLE);
567 cr->SetArmor(_currentIllusion);
568 }
569 }
570
571 EntryCheckPredicate pred(NPC_BRAIN_OF_YOGG_SARON);
572 summons.DoAction(_currentIllusion, pred);
573
574 if (_isIllusionReversed)
575 _currentIllusion = _currentIllusion == 3 ? 1 : (_currentIllusion + 1);
576 else
577 _currentIllusion = _currentIllusion == 1 ? 3 : (_currentIllusion - 1);
578 }
579
580 void SpellSounds()
581 {
582 if (urand(0, 9))
583 return;
584
585 if (urand(0, 1))
586 {
587 me->Yell(_secondPhase ? "Tremble, mortals, before the coming of the end!" : "Yes! YES! Show them no mercy! Give no pause to your attacks!", LANG_UNIVERSAL);
588 me->PlayDirectSound(_secondPhase ? SARA_P2_CAST2 : SARA_P1_CAST1);
589 }
590 else
591 {
592 me->Yell(_secondPhase ? "Suffocate upon your own hate!" : "Let hatred and rage guide your blows!", LANG_UNIVERSAL);
593 me->PlayDirectSound(_secondPhase ? SARA_P2_CAST1 : SARA_P1_CAST2);
594 }
595 }
596
597 void KilledUnit(Unit* who) override
598 {
599 if (who->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
600 return;
601
602 if (urand(0, 1))
603 {

638 void DoAction(int32 param) override
639 {
640 if (param == ACTION_BRAIN_DAMAGED)
641 {
642 summons.DoAction(ACTION_REMOVE_STUN);
643
644 EntryCheckPredicate pred2(NPC_YOGG_SARON);
645 summons.DoAction(ACTION_YOGG_SARON_START_P3, pred2);
646
647 EntryCheckPredicate pred3(NPC_THORIM_KEEPER);
648 summons.DoAction(ACTION_THORIM_START_STORM, pred3);
649
650 if (!(_keepersGUID[0] && _keepersGUID[1] && _keepersGUID[2] && _keepersGUID[3]) && me->GetMap()->Is25ManRaid())
651 summons.DoAction(ACTION_YOGG_SARON_HARD_MODE, pred2);
652
653 summons.DespawnEntry(NPC_DEATH_ORB);
654 events.SetPhase(EVENT_PHASE_THREE);
655
656 me->RemoveAllAuras();
657 me->SetVisible(false);
658 return;
659 }
660 else if (param == ACTION_YOGG_SARON_DEATH)
661 {
662 summons.DespawnEntry(NPC_VOICE_OF_YOGG_SARON);
663 summons.DespawnEntry(NPC_BRAIN_OF_YOGG_SARON);
664 summons.DespawnEntry(NPC_MIMIRON_KEEPER);
665 summons.DespawnEntry(NPC_HODIR_KEEPER);
666 summons.DespawnEntry(NPC_FREYA_KEEPER);
667 summons.DespawnEntry(NPC_THORIM_KEEPER);
668 summons.DespawnEntry(NPC_SANITY_WELL);
669 Unit::Kill(me, me);
670 return;
671 }
672
673 // Determine shatter duration
674 if (param <= 0)
675 return;
676
677 // Illusion shatters (param - stun time)
678 WorldPacket data;
679 ChatHandler::BuildChatPacket(data, CHAT_MSG_RAID_BOSS_EMOTE, LANG_UNIVERSAL, me, nullptr, "Illusion shatters and a path to the central chamber opens!");
680 me->SendMessageToSetInRange(&data, 500, false);

682 uint32 timer = events.GetNextEventTime(EVENT_SARA_P2_OPEN_PORTALS);
683 uint32 portalTime = (timer > events.GetTimer() ? timer - events.GetTimer() : 0);
684 events.DelayEvents(param + 100);
685 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_SARA_P2_OPEN_PORTALS, portalTime, 0, EVENT_PHASE_TWO);
686 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARA_P2_REMOVE_STUN, param, 0, EVENT_PHASE_TWO);
687 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_SHATTERED_ILLUSION, true);
688 }

718 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
719 {
720 if (_initFight)
721 {
722 _initFight += diff;
723 if (_initFight > 5000)
724 {
725 if (Unit* target = SelectTargetFromPlayerList(90))
726 {
727 _initFight = 0;
728 InitFight(target);
729 }
730 else
731 _initFight = 1;
732 }
733 return;
734 }
735
736 if (!SelectTargetFromPlayerList(90, SPELL_INSANE1))
737 {
738 m_pInstance->DoRemoveAurasDueToSpellOnPlayers(SPELL_INSANE1);
739 EnterEvadeMode(EVADE_REASON_OTHER);
740 return;
741 }
742
743 if (_p2TalkTimer)
744 {
745 _p2TalkTimer += diff;
746 if (_p2TalkTimer >= 4000 && _p2TalkTimer < 20000)
747 {
748 EntryCheckPredicate pred(NPC_OMINOUS_CLOUD);
749 summons.DoAction(ACTION_UNSUMMON_CLOUDS, pred);
750 me->Yell("The monster in your nightmares.", LANG_UNIVERSAL);
751 _p2TalkTimer = 20000;
752 }
753 else if (_p2TalkTimer >= 25000 && _p2TalkTimer < 40000)
754 {
755 summons.DespawnEntry(NPC_OMINOUS_CLOUD);
756 me->Yell("The fiend of a thousand faces.", LANG_UNIVERSAL);
757 _p2TalkTimer = 40000;
758 }
759 else if (_p2TalkTimer >= 44500 && _p2TalkTimer < 60000)
760 {
761 me->Yell("Cower before my true form.", LANG_UNIVERSAL);
762 _p2TalkTimer = 60000;
763 }
764 else if (_p2TalkTimer >= 64000)
765 {
766 EntryCheckPredicate pred(NPC_YOGG_SARON);
767 summons.DoAction(ACTION_YOGG_SARON_START_YELL, pred);
768 _p2TalkTimer = 0;
769 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARA_P2_START, 500, 0, EVENT_PHASE_TWO);
770 }
771 return;
772 }
773
774 events.Update(diff);
775 if (me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING))
776 return;
777
778 switch(events.ExecuteEvent())
779 {
780 case EVENT_SARA_P1_DOORS_CLOSE:
781 // Whispers of YS

789 break;
790 case EVENT_SARA_P1_SUMMON:
791 events.RepeatEvent(20000 - (std::min(_summonedGuardiansCount, (uint8)5) * 2000));
792 ++_summonedGuardiansCount;
793 InformCloud();
794 break;
795 case EVENT_SARA_P1_SPELLS:
796 {
797 uint32 spell = RAND(SPELL_SARAS_ANGER_TARGET_SELECTOR, SPELL_SARAS_BLESSING_TARGET_SELECTOR, SPELL_SARAS_FAVOR_TARGET_SELECTOR);
798 me->CastCustomSpell(spell, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 1, nullptr, false);
799 SpellSounds();
800 events.RepeatEvent(me->GetMap()->Is25ManRaid() ? urand(0, 3000) : 4000 + urand(0, 2000));
801 break;
802 }
803 case EVENT_SARA_P2_START:
804 {
805 EntryCheckPredicate pred(NPC_YOGG_SARON);
806 summons.DoAction(ACTION_YOGG_SARON_APPEAR, pred);
807 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_SARA_P2_SPAWN_START_TENTACLES, 500, 0, EVENT_PHASE_TWO);
808
809 // Spawn Brain!
810 me->SummonCreature(NPC_BRAIN_OF_YOGG_SARON, 1981.3f, -25.43f, 265);
811 break;
812 }
813 case EVENT_SARA_P2_MALADY:
814 me->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_MALADY_OF_THE_MIND, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 1, me, false);
815 events.RepeatEvent(20000);
816 break;
817 case EVENT_SARA_P2_PSYCHOSIS:
818 SpellSounds();
819 me->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_PSYCHOSIS, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 1, me, false);
820 events.RepeatEvent(3500);
821 break;
822 case EVENT_SARA_P2_DEATH_RAY:
823 SummonDeathOrbs();
824 events.RepeatEvent(20000);
825 break;
826 case EVENT_SARA_P2_SUMMON_T1: // CRUSHER
827 SpawnTentacle(NPC_CRUSHER_TENTACLE);
828 events.RepeatEvent((50000 + urand(0, 10000)) * _summonSpeed);
829 break;
830 case EVENT_SARA_P2_SUMMON_T2: // CONSTRICTOR
831 SpawnTentacle(NPC_CONSTRICTOR_TENTACLE);
832 events.RepeatEvent((15000 + urand(0, 5000)) * _summonSpeed);
833 break;
834 case EVENT_SARA_P2_SUMMON_T3: // CORRUPTOR
835 SpawnTentacle(NPC_CORRUPTOR_TENTACLE);
836 events.RepeatEvent((30000 + urand(0, 10000)) * _summonSpeed);
837 break;
838 case EVENT_SARA_P2_BRAIN_LINK:
839 me->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_BRAIN_LINK, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 1, me, false);

858 me->SetDisplayId(SARA_TRANSFORM_MODEL);

860 me->SendMonsterMove(me->GetPositionX(), me->GetPositionY(), 355, 2000, SPLINEFLAG_FLYING);
861 me->SetPosition(me->GetPositionX(), me->GetPositionY(), 355, me->GetOrientation());

864 SpawnTentacle(NPC_CONSTRICTOR_TENTACLE);
865 SpawnTentacle(NPC_CORRUPTOR_TENTACLE);
866 SpawnTentacle(NPC_CORRUPTOR_TENTACLE);
867
868 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARA_P2_MALADY, 7000, 0, EVENT_PHASE_TWO);
869 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARA_P2_PSYCHOSIS, 3000, 0, EVENT_PHASE_TWO);
870 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARA_P2_DEATH_RAY, 15000, 0, EVENT_PHASE_TWO);
871 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SARA_P2_SUMMON_T1, 50000 + urand(0, 10000), 0, EVENT_PHASE_TWO);

881 }

1350 void DoAction(int32 param) override
1351 {
1352 if (param == ACTION_DESPAWN_ADDS)
1353 {
1354 summons.DespawnAll();
1355 return;
1356 }
1357 else if (param == ACTION_INFLUENCE_TENTACLE_DIED)
1358 {
1359 _tentacleCount++;
1360 if (_tentacleCount >= 7 /*TENTACLES COUNT*/)
1361 {
1362 // Stun
1363 if (me->GetInstanceScript())
1364 if(Creature* sara = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, me->GetInstanceScript()->GetGuidData(NPC_SARA)))
1365 sara->AI()->DoAction(MINUTE * IN_MILLISECONDS - std::min((uint32)MINUTE * IN_MILLISECONDS, _induceTimer));
1366
1367 _induceTimer = 0;
1368 summons.DespawnEntry(NPC_LAUGHING_SKULL);
1369 if (GameObject* go = me->FindNearestGameObject(GO_CHAMBER_ILLUSION_DOORS + _activeIllusion, 150.0f))
1370 go->SetGoState(GO_STATE_ACTIVE);
1371 }
1372 return;
1373 }
1374 else if (param == ACTION_REMOVE_STUN)
1375 return;
1376
1377 summons.DespawnAll();
1378 switch(param)
1379 {
1380 case ACTION_ILLUSION_STORMWIND:
1381 PrepareStormwindIllusion();
1382 break;
1383 case ACTION_ILLUSION_DRAGONS:
1384 PrepareChamberIllusion();
1385 break;
1386 case ACTION_ILLUSION_ICECROWN:
1387 PrepareIceCrownIllusion();
1388 break;
1389 }
1390
1391 for (uint32 i = GO_CHAMBER_ILLUSION_DOORS; i <= GO_STORMWIND_ILLUSION_DOORS; ++i)
1392 if (GameObject* go = me->FindNearestGameObject(i, 150.0f))
1393 go->SetGoState(GO_STATE_READY);
1394
1395 _activeIllusion = param - 1;
1396 _tentacleCount = 0;
1397 _induceTimer = 1;
1398
1399 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_INDUCE_MADNESS, false);
1400 }
1401
1402 uint32 GetData(uint32 param) const override
1403 {
1404 if (param == DATA_GET_CURRENT_ILLUSION)
1405 return _activeIllusion + 1;
1406
1407 return 0;
1408 }
1409
1410 void DamageTaken(Unit* who, uint32& damage, DamageEffectType, SpellSchoolMask) override
1411 {
1412 if (_tentacleCount < 7) // if all tentacles aren't killed
1413 {
1414 damage = 0;
1415 if (who)
1416 Unit::Kill(who, who);
1417 return;
1418 }
1419
1420 if (!_brainDamaged)
1421 {
1422 // START PHASE 3
1423 if (me->HealthBelowPctDamaged(30, damage))
1424 {
1425 me->SetRegeneratingHealth(false);
1426 _EnterEvadeMode();
1427 _brainDamaged = true;
1428
1429 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_BRAIN_HURT_VISUAL, true);
1430 if (me->GetInstanceScript())
1431 if(Creature* sara = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, me->GetInstanceScript()->GetGuidData(NPC_SARA)))
1432 sara->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_BRAIN_DAMAGED);
1433 }
1434 }
1435 }
1436
1437 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
1438 {
1439 if (_induceTimer)
1440 _induceTimer += diff;
1441 }
1442 };

2350 Map::PlayerList const& pList = GetUnitOwner()->GetMap()->GetPlayers();
2351 uint8 _offset = urand(0, pList.getSize() - 1);
2352 uint8 _counter = 0;
2353 for(Map::PlayerList::const_iterator itr = pList.begin(); itr != pList.end(); ++itr, ++_counter)
2354 {
2355 if (itr->GetSource() == GetUnitOwner() || GetUnitOwner()->GetDistance(itr->GetSource()) > 50.0f || !itr->GetSource()->IsAlive() || itr->GetSource()->IsGameMaster())
2356 continue;
2357
2358 if (_counter <= _offset || !target)
2359 target = itr->GetSource();
2360 else
2361 break;
2362 }

2365 SetDuration(0);
2366 else
2367 _targetGUID = target->GetGUID();

2379 Unit* _target = ObjectAccessor::GetUnit(*owner, _targetGUID);
2380 if (!_target || !_target->IsAlive() || std::fabs(owner->GetPositionZ() - _target->GetPositionZ()) > 10.0f) // Target or owner underground
2381 {
2382 SetDuration(0);
2383 return;
2384 }
2385
2386 if (owner->GetDistance(_target) > 20.0f)
2387 {
2388 owner->CastSpell(_target, SPELL_BRAIN_LINK_DAMAGE, true);
2389 owner->CastSpell(owner, SPELL_BRAIN_LINK_DAMAGE, true);
2390 }
2391 else
2392 owner->CastSpell(_target, SPELL_BRAIN_LINK_OK, true);
2393 }
